  <summary date="2021-06-02T16:41:26Z" status="Introduced in House">CHAMPVA Children's Care Protection Act of 2021

This bill provides that a child shall be eligible for medical care under the Civilian Health and Medical Program of the Department of Veterans Affairs (CHAMPVA) until the child's 26th birthday, regardless of the child's marital status.</summary>
